                    </a>
                </div>
                <div id="sq2" class="accordion-body collapse">
                    <div class="accordion-inner">
                        <ol>
                            <li class="help-li">Navigate to the Surveys page, click the survey you want to edit, and click the button labeled "Edit".<br/><img src="~/Content/images/faq/edit_survey1.png" class="help-img"></li>
                            <li class="help-li">From this screen, edit anything that needs to be changed. If you need help with what options on this screen do what, please see the above question.</li>
                            <li class="help-li">When done, make sure to hit the button labeled "Save" to save your changes.</li>
                        </ol>
