                    <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#surveyAccordion" href="#sq3">
                        What is duplicating a survey?
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div id="sq3" class="accordion-body collapse">
                    <div class="accordion-inner">
                        Duplicating a survey allows you to create a copy of a survey. This should be done if you want to make a new survey that's similar to another survey, but don't want to make any changes to the original survey.
                        To duplicate a survey:
                        <ol>
                            <li class="help-li">Select the survey you wish to duplicate and click the button labeled "Duplicate".<br/><img src="~/Content/images/faq/duplicate1.png" class="help-img" /></li>
                            <li class="help-li">After clicking, the survey will be duplicated!<br/><img src="~/Content/images/faq/duplicate2.png" class="help-img" /></li>
                        </ol>
                        <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#surveyAccordion" href="#sq3">
                            Close Question
                        </a> | <a href="#">Back to top</a>
                        <hr />
                    </div>
