                            <li class="help-li">You will be taken to a confirmation screen, click the button labeled "Delete" to permanently delete the survey or "Back to list" to go back to the survey list.</li>
                            <li class="help-li">The survey is now deleted!<img src="~/Content/images/faq/delete2.png" class="help-img"/></li>
                        </ol>
