                        <p>A Choice Image is an image that will go to the right of a choice in a survey question. To find out how to use a Choice Image in a survey, go to the above question named "How do I create a survey?"<br/><img src="~/Content/images/faq/images1.png" class="help-img"/></p>
                        <p>An Exhibit Image is an image that will go with an Exhibit question in a survey. To find out how to use an Exhibit Image, go to the "How do I create an Exhibit?" question below this question.<br/><img src="~/Content/images/faq/images4.png" class="help-img" /></p>
                        <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#surveyAccordion" href="#iq3">
